{"tid":1469301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"100毛 講不割席","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:53.000Z","uid":67813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2622c276c8fc51f1ace5403a8043548fbade507d","tid":1469301,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"有冇留意，一直以來親建制都係極團結的。<br />\n你先唔好理佢哋嘅團結係唔係為咗利益，<br />\n係唔係冇自由意志，<br />\n總之佢哋就係好團結。<br />\n甚至乎佢哋嘅成功，就係源於團結。<br />\n你見佢哋其實係甚少會公開批評同路建制仔。<br />\n(有時都會嘅，但比起嚟真係好少)<br />\n好似何姓元朗大總統啲行為咁癲，<br />\n好多親建制中產暗地裏可能都唔認同佢，<br />\n但佢哋冇公開叫佢應該點、唔應該點。<br />\n佢哋最能體現到咩叫不篤灰不割蓆。"},{"pid":"9706d7919f2d5b756e5a8f1eb95bbd52d911d069","tid":1469301,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5ea390b02342bc0106866ad5607989546be8abf9","tid":1469301,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6bf260354f04fe76f621376816b992302088f9ce","tid":1469301,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0a2c69910129fb91fe3fc9837d64a79f92709ebb","tid":1469301,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"4"}]}